
1) Random recipe
   "https://api.spoonacular.com/recipes/random?number={NUMBER OF RECIPES}&apiKey={API_KEY}"

2) give All the Recipe 
  "https://api.spoonacular.com/recipes/complexSearch?query=snack&apiKey={key}&number={number of product}"

3) find the details of particular recipe by ID
"https://api.spoonacular.com/recipes/{ID}/information?apiKey="

4) get similar recipe
"https://api.spoonacular.com/recipes/{id}/similar?apiKey="

5) search grocery product
"https://api.spoonacular.com/food/products/search?query={food-name}&number=2"

6) ChatBot 
"https://api.spoonacular.com/food/converse?text=tell+me+a+joke"


